# Microsoft Sentinel Integration with Azure VM

## Introduction
This project demonstrates how to integrate an Azure Virtual Machine with Microsoft Sentinel. It includes steps for installing the Log Analytics Agent, configuring data collection, and setting up a Kusto Query Language (KQL) rule to monitor successful login events every 5 minutes.

## Installation
1. Install the Log Analytics Agent on your Azure VM.
2. Configure the agent to collect the necessary data.
3. Set up data connectors in Microsoft Sentinel.

## Usage
Run the KQL query to monitor successful login events every 5 minutes and configure alerts based on your requirements.


